<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٥٣٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5889">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ كَثِيرٍ </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6361">مَنْصُورٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2238">سَالِمٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ <span class="c2">«تَسَمَّوْا بِاسْمِي وَلَا تَكْتَنُوا بِكُنْيَتِي.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>